{
  "_comment": "Single source of truth for the bundled upstream skills. Add/swap/remove a skill = edit one entry here, then run scripts/sync-upstreams.sh. scripts/check-upstreams.py bumps each `ref` to the newest release per its `update` policy. The sync + patch scripts read everything below; no skill-specific code lives in the scripts.",
